---
// About — Dean Cascione, master luthier
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets';
import deanImg from '~/assets/images/dean_cascione_custom_guitars.jpg';
import nammImg from '~/assets/images/dean_cascione_seymour_duncan_floyd_rose.jpg';
---

<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">The Luthier</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Every guitar<br />tells a story.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about">
      <div class="about__media">
        <Picture
          src={deanImg}
          alt="Master Luthier Dean Cascione in his shop"
          loading="lazy"
          widths={[320, 480, 640, 800]}
          sizes="(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 50vw"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="about__body">
        <p>
          <strong>Dean Cascione</strong> is a master luthier and professional guitarist
          who has been hand-building instruments and performing world-class
          fretboard scalloping since 2004. Every instrument that leaves the
          DC Custom Guitars shop is built, finished, wired, assembled, and
          set up by Dean himself.
        </p>
        <p>
          From a single sketch on a napkin to the final setup, you work
          hand-in-hand with Dean through the entire build process. You choose
          the body wood, neck profile, fretboard, inlays, pickups, bridge,
          tuners, hardware, and finish. The result: a guitar that looks,
          feels, and sounds like <em>exactly</em> what you imagined.
        </p>
        <p>
          DC Custom has also been trusted by some of the most respected
          names in shred — and Dean's scalloping clients include pro players
          and OEM companies worldwide.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="about__quote">
          "Isn't it time you stopped playing someone else's custom shop
          signature model and started playing your own?"
          <span class="about__quote-attr">— Dean Cascione</span>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about__partners">
      <p class="about__partners-lead">
        We've teamed up with the <strong>BEST manufacturers</strong> of guitar
        tremolos, pickups, frets, strings, string nuts, strap locks, and tuners
        to bring you the highest quality and best sounding instruments on the
        planet.
      </p>
      <figure class="about__figure">
        <Picture
          src={nammImg}
          alt="Dean Cascione at NAMM with Floyd Rose and Seymour Duncan"
          loading="lazy"
          widths={[480, 768, 1024, 1280, 1600]}
          sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 1280px, 100vw"
        />
        <figcaption>
          Dean "DC" Cascione at NAMM with Floyd Rose &amp; Seymour Duncan!
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
